<div class="center jumbotron">
  <h1>Welcome to Memepedia!</h1>
  <p>
    The homepage serves the purpose to present all the features of the website to the users.
  </p>
  <p>
    Users can generate a random meme from the meme library of the website through the "Show Me Some Memes" button. A user account can be signed up through the "Sign Up!" button.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you need additional help or information, you can find relevant information through "Help" and "Contact" on the header and footer navigation bars. A weekly meme series is also accessible through the "Weekly Series" link.
  </p>
  
  <%= link_to "Show Me Some Memes", '#', class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
  <%= link_to "Sign up!", signup_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
</div>

<figure>
  <%= link_to image_tag("simpsons/#{@index}.jpg", alt: "sample meme", class: "img-responsive center-block") %>
  <figcaption>source: <%= @source_line %></figcaption>
</figure>
